    <title>Fedora-基于Hexo搭建博客</title>
    <link href="http://samuelbaizg.github.io/2019/02/24/Fedora%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8EHexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>http://samuelbaizg.github.io/2019/02/24/Fedora基于Hexo搭建博客/</id>
    <published>2019-02-24T12:28:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-03T10:32:12.584Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install nodejs</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install npm</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo npm install hexo-cli -g</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="生成博客"><a href="#生成博客" class="headerlink" title="生成博客"></a>生成博客</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd ~</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># hexo init blog</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd blog</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># npm install</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># hexo server</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="配置站点"><a href="#配置站点" class="headerlink" title="配置站点"></a>配置站点</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># vim _config.yml</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>属性值参照hexo官方文档-<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/。小提示：language为themes/next/languages/目录下的不带扩展名的文件名，如zh-Hans。" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/。小提示：language为themes/next/languages/目录下的不带扩展名的文件名，如zh-Hans。</a></p><h1 id="安装Next主题"><a href="#安装Next主题" class="headerlink" title="安装Next主题"></a>安装Next主题</h1><ul><li>官网下载Next最新版本（<a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next）" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next）</a></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># wget https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/archive/v5.1.4.tar.gz</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>解压v5.1.4.tar.gz至站点的themes目录下，并将解压后的文件夹名称更改为next</li><li>更改站点配置文件_config.yml中的theme为next，如下：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme : next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>更改themes/next/_config.yml中的配置，属性值参照next官方文档(<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://theme-next.iissnan.com</a>)</li><li>更改_config.yml后，可以用yaml-lint校验语法</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd ~/blog 'hexo site root directory'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo npm install -g yaml-lint</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># yamllint themes/next/_config.yml</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>设置 RSS<ul><li>安装hexo-generator-feed</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd 'hexo blog root directory'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>更改next配置文件_config.yml，设定 rss 字段的值</li></ul><ul><li>设置文章版权信息<ul><li>在目录_config.yml中，设置url：</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># URL</span><br><span class="line">## If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as &apos;http://yoursite.com/child&apos; and root as &apos;/child/&apos;</span><br><span class="line">url: http://samuelbaizg.github.io</span><br><span class="line">root: /</span><br><span class="line">permalink: :year/:month/:day/:title/</span><br><span class="line">permalink_defaults:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>在目录themes/_config.yml，打开文章版权设置和license：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post_copyright:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  license: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</span><br><span class="line">  license_url: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>发文章时增加版权信息copyright: true，如下：</li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Fedora-基于Hexo搭建博客</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-02-24 20:28:58</span><br><span class="line">categories: [其它]</span><br><span class="line">tags: [Hexo]</span><br><span class="line">copyright : true</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>修改版权内容和样式<br>修改themes/next/layout/_macro/post-copyright.swig和themes/next/source/css/_common/components/post/post-copyright.styl文件即可</li><li>Ctrl+C或者鼠标右键点击复制时，拷贝内容增加版权信息<br>待补充</li></ul><ul><li>修改主题宽度<br>主题变量定义/themes/next/source/css/_variables/主题名.styl，如/themes/next/source/css/_variables/Gemini.styl，如下：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// --------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">$body-bg-color                    = #eee</span><br><span class="line">$main-desktop                     = 100%</span><br><span class="line">$sidebar-desktop                  = 240px</span><br><span class="line">$content-desktop                  = calc(100% - 252px)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中的$main-desktop为主题桌面跨度，可根据自己喜好设置，如75%，85%，100%等任意值。</p><ul><li>修改hexo new创建的post默认模板<br>修改scaffolds/post.md文件即可。</li></ul><h1 id="部署到Github"><a href="#部署到Github" class="headerlink" title="部署到Github"></a>部署到Github</h1><ul><li>在github上注册账号，比如：samuelbaizg</li><li>在_config.yml, 配置github部署信息，比如：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/samuelbaizg/samuelbaizg.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>运行如下命令部署到Github</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd ~/blog</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># hexo clean</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># hexo generate</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># hexo deploy</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
