    <title>Fedora-安装Python开发环境</title>
    <link href="http://samuelbaizg.github.io/2019/02/16/Fedora%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Python%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
    <id>http://samuelbaizg.github.io/2019/02/16/Fedora安装Python开发环境/</id>
    <published>2019-02-16T13:54:57.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-03T10:31:53.493Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装Visual-Studio-Code"><a href="#安装Visual-Studio-Code" class="headerlink" title="安装Visual Studio Code"></a>安装Visual Studio Code</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo rpm --import https://packages.microsoft.com/keys/microsoft.asc</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo sh -c 'echo -e "[code]\nname=Visual Studio Code\nbaseurl=https://packages.microsoft.com/yumrepos/vscode\nenabled=1\ngpgcheck=1\ngpgkey=https://packages.microsoft.com/keys/microsoft.asc" &gt; /etc/yum.repos.d/vscode.repo' </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf check-update</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install code</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装配置RPMFusion"><a href="#安装配置RPMFusion" class="headerlink" title="安装配置RPMFusion"></a>安装配置RPMFusion</h1><ul><li>安装RPMFusion安装包</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck http://download1.rpmfusion.org/free/fedora/rpmfusion-free-release-$(rpm -E %fedora).noarch.rpm http://download1.rpmfusion.org/nonfree/fedora/rpmfusion-nonfree-release-$(rpm -E %fedora).noarch.rpm</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>修改RPMFusion源指向清华TUNA镜像<br>修改 /etc/yum.repos.d/ 目录下以 rpmfusion 开头、以 .repo 结尾的文件, 将其中的baseurl=开头的行等号后面链接中的 <a href="http://download1.rpmfusion.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://download1.rpmfusion.org/</a> 替换为<a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/rpmfusion/，其他属性值保持不变，修改后的baseurl和metalink样例如下：" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/rpmfusion/，其他属性值保持不变，修改后的baseurl和metalink样例如下：</a></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[rpmfusion-free]</span><br><span class="line">baseurl=https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/rpmfusion/free/fedora/releases/$releasever/Everything/$basearch/os/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="升级Fedora软件"><a href="#升级Fedora软件" class="headerlink" title="升级Fedora软件"></a>升级Fedora软件</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf upgrade --refresh</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf isntall vim</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="gedit支持中文"><a href="#gedit支持中文" class="headerlink" title="gedit支持中文"></a>gedit支持中文</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># gsettings set org.gnome.gedit.preferences.encodings candidate-encodings "['GB18030','GB2312','GBK', 'UTF-8', 'CURRENT', 'ISO-8859-15', 'UTF-16']"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装libeoffice中文语言包"><a href="#安装libeoffice中文语言包" class="headerlink" title="安装libeoffice中文语言包"></a>安装libeoffice中文语言包</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install libreoffice-langpack-zh-Han*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装p7z等压缩插件"><a href="#安装p7z等压缩插件" class="headerlink" title="安装p7z等压缩插件"></a>安装p7z等压缩插件</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install p7zip p7zip-plugins unrar unzip</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装gnome-tewaks"><a href="#安装gnome-tewaks" class="headerlink" title="安装gnome-tewaks"></a>安装gnome-tewaks</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install gnome-tweaks</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装Chrome"><a href="#安装Chrome" class="headerlink" title="安装Chrome"></a>安装Chrome</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install fedora-workstation-repositories</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf config-manager --set-enabled google-chrome</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install google-chrome-stable</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装Python3和Pycharm"><a href="#安装Python3和Pycharm" class="headerlink" title="安装Python3和Pycharm"></a>安装Python3和Pycharm</h1><ul><li>安装依赖库</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install gcc openssl-devel bzip2-devel</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装Python（Fedora29默认安装了Python3.7.2）</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd ~/Downloads/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.6.7/Python-3.6.7.tgz</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># tar xzf Python-3.6.7.tgz</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd Python-3.6.7</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ./configure --enable-optimizations</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo make altinstall</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># rm -rf Python-3.6.7</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo pip3.6 install virtualenv</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># python3.6 --version</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo pip3.6 install virtualenv</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo pip3.6 install --upgrade pip</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>备注：make altinstall避免替换默认的/usr/bin/python。</p><ul><li>安装Pycharm<br>官网下载Pycharm Fedora安装包，解压到某一个目录下即可</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd ~/Downloads/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># wget https://download.jetbrains.com/python/pycharm-community-2018.3.4.tar.gz</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># tar xzvf pycharm-community-2018.3.4.tar.gz</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo mv pycharm-community-2018.3.4 /usr/local</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo ln -s /usr/local/pycharm-community-2018.3.4/ pycharm</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>建立Pycharm桌面快捷链接<ul><li>在/usr/share/applications目录下建立Pycharm.desktop文件</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /usr/share/applications/Pycharm.desktop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>拷贝如下内容到Pycharm.desktop中，并保存。</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Desktop Entry]</span><br><span class="line">Type=Application</span><br><span class="line">Name=Pycharm</span><br><span class="line">GenericName=Pycharm3</span><br><span class="line">Comment=Pycharm3:The Python IDE</span><br><span class="line">Exec=sh /usr/local/pycharm/bin/pycharm.sh</span><br><span class="line">Icon=/usr/local/pycharm/bin/pycharm.png</span><br><span class="line">Terminal=pycharm</span><br><span class="line">Categories=Pycharm;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>备注：上述内容需要将Exec和Icon改成文件实际的路径</p><ul><li>在应用程序菜单里可以找到Pycharm，点击打开Pycharm程序,也可以右键将Pycharm添加到Favorite菜单中</li></ul><h2 id="安装MySQL"><a href="#安装MySQL" class="headerlink" title="安装MySQL"></a>安装MySQL</h2><ul><li>安装MySQL Server</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install libaio</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd ~/Downloads/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># wget https://cdn.mysql.com//Downloads/MySQL-5.7/mysql-5.7.25-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.gz</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># tar xzvf mysql-5.7.25-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.gz</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo mv mysql-5.7.25-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64 /usr/local</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo ln -s /usr/local/mysql-5.7.24-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64/ mysql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo service sssd stop</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo groupadd mysql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo useradd -r -g mysql -s /bin/false mysql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd mysql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># mkdir mysql-files</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo chown mysql:mysql mysql-files</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo chmod 750 mysql-files</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># bin/mysqld --initialize --user=mysql</span></span><br><span class="line">记住行末尾的root的临时密码</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># bin/mysql_ssl_rsa_setup</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># bin/mysqld_safe --user=mysql &amp;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo cp support-files/mysql.server /etc/init.d/mysql.server</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># bin/mysql -uroot -p</span></span><br><span class="line">输入root的临时秘密</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; alter user <span class="string">'root'</span>@<span class="string">'localhost'</span> identified by <span class="string">'123456'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; use mysql;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; update user <span class="built_in">set</span> user.Host=<span class="string">'%'</span> <span class="built_in">where</span> user.User=<span class="string">'root'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; flush privileges;</span><br><span class="line">mysql &gt; quit;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装MySQL Workbench</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cd ~/Downloads/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># wget https://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/MySQLGUITools/mysql-workbench-community-8.0.15-1.fc29.x86_64.rpm</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sudo dnf install mysql-workbench-community-8.0.15-1.fc29.x86_64.rpm</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
